spec_data.Name: atlas-corei2-devel
spec_data.Description:
This package contains shared and static versions of the ATLAS
(Automatically Tuned Linear Algebra Software) libraries compiled with
optimizations for the corei2 (Ivy/Sandy bridge) CPUs.

spec_data.Summary: Development libraries for ATLAS for Corei2 (Ivy/Sandy bridge) CPUs
